or violations of an executive order issued by the governor under the provisions of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 473.8}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine is seventy dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E17_2E4_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E17_2E4_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Alcoholic beverage violations.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For violations of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 123.49, subsection 2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, paragraph }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fh\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine for a licensee or permittee is one thousand nine hundred twenty-five dollars, and the scheduled fine for a person who is employed by a licensee or permittee is six hundred forty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E17_2E5_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E17_2E5_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Violations related to smoking, tobacco, tobacco products, alternative nicotine products, vapor products, and cigarettes.}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For violations described in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 142D.9, subsection 1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine is fifty dollars, and is a civil penalty, and the crime services surcharge under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 911.1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall not be added to the penalty, and the court costs pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 805.9, subsection 6}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, shall not be imposed. If the civil penalty assessed for a violation described in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 142D.9, subsection 1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, is not paid in a timely manner, a citation shall be issued for the violation in the manner provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 804.1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{. However, a person under age eighteen shall not be detained in a secure facility for failure to pay the civil penalty. The complainant shall not be charged a filing fee.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For violations of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 453A.2, subsection 1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, by an employee of a retailer, the scheduled fine is as follows:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a first offense, the scheduled fine is one hundred thirty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a second offense, the scheduled fine is three hundred twenty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a third or subsequent offense, the scheduled fine is six hundred forty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{c.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For violations of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 453A.2, subsection 2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine is as follows and is a civil penalty, and the crime services surcharge under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 911.1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall not be added to the penalty, and the court costs pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 805.9, subsection 6}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, shall not be imposed:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a first offense, the scheduled fine is seventy dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a second offense, the scheduled fine is one hundred thirty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a third or subsequent offense, the scheduled fine is three hundred twenty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{d.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(1)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For violations of }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 204.14E}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine is as follows:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(a)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a first offense, the scheduled fine is seventy dollars.}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(b)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a second offense, the scheduled fine is one hundred thirty-five dollars.}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(c)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{If the violation is a third or subsequent offense, the scheduled fine is three hundred twenty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The fine shall be imposed as a civil penalty.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(3)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The crime services surcharge under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 911.1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall not be added to the penalty, and the court costs pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 805.9, subsection 6}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, shall not be imposed.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(4)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Notwithstanding }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 805.12}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, any civil penalty paid under this paragraph shall be retained by the city or county enforcing the violation. }}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{4.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E17_2E6_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E17_2E6_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Electrical or mechanical amusement device violations.}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For violations of legal age for operating an electrical or mechanical amusement device required to be registered as provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 99B.53}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 99B.57, subsection 1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine is three hundred twenty-five dollars. Failure to pay the fine by a person under the age of eighteen shall not result in the person being detained in a secure facility.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For first offense violations concerning electrical or mechanical amusement devices as provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 99B.54, subsection 2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine is three hundred twenty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{5.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E17_2E7_2E1_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E17_2E7_2E1_2E2}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Gambling violations.}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{a.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For violations of legal age for gambling wagering under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 99D.11, subsection 7}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 99F.9, subsection 5}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, and }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 725.19, subsection 1}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine is six hundred forty-five dollars. Failure to pay the fine by a person under the age of eighteen shall not result in the person being detained in a secure facility.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For legal age violations for entering or attempting to enter a facility under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 99F.9, subsection 6}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, the scheduled fine is six hundred forty-five dollars. Failure to pay the fine by a person under the age of eighteen shall not result in the person being detained in a secure facility.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{6.}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E17_2E8_2E1_2E2}